<paragraph blockId="179.[189,1399,1468,1530]" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">
This species is named in honor of Dr. Yalin Zhang, who has contributed extensively to knowledge of the 
<collectingRegion box="[189,285,1504,1530]" country="Republic of the Congo" name="Orientale" pageId="179" pageNumber="180">Oriental</collectingRegion>
leafhopper fauna.
</paragraph>
